$SET XTQA YES

$SET VAR_UC YES 
$ SET OBJ AUTO
$ SET MID_YEAR YES
$ SET OBLONG YES
$SET DAMAGE NO
$ SET STAGES NO
$SET SOLVEDA 'YES'
$SET VARCOST LIN
$ SET DSC NO
$SET DATAGDX YES





* merge declarations & data
$   ONMULTI


* the times-slices MUST come 1st to ensure ordering OK
$BATINCLUDE demos_002_ts.dd


*<perform fixed declarations>
$SET BOTIME 1980

* declare the (system/user) empties

$IF NOT DECLARED REG_BNDCST $Abort "You need to use TIMES v2.3.1 or higher"


$BATINCLUDE base.dd

SET MILESTONYR /2005,2006/;
$SET RUN_NAME 'demos_002'






$ SET VEDAVDD 'YES'


* do the rest
$ BATINCLUDE maindrv.mod mod
